title: Authorizes the village of Port Jefferson to discontinue the use of certain city lands as parkland and to alienate and convey such lands
summary: Authorizes the village of Port Jefferson, town of Brookhaven, county of Suffolk to discontinue the use of certain city lands as parkland and to alienate and convey such lands.
actClause: AN ACT to authorize the village of Port Jefferson, town of Brookhaven, county of Suffolk to discontinue the use of certain city lands as parkland and to alienate and convey such lands
